Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.95,CC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}A truly breathtaking display of cardio begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.95,0:00:03.26,CC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look at that blistering pace. Absolutely electric.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.26,0:00:04.56,CC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He is definitely winning this race against himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.56,0:00:05.86,CC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Still running. The momentum is truly staggering.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.86,0:00:07.17,CC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The sheer athleticism is almost too much to handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.17,0:00:09.12,CC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And he exits, leaving us all in his dust.
